subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
lead_paragraph: Gordon won the AAA 400 at Dover International Speedway in Maryland, the third race in the Chase for the Sprint Cup championship. Gordon gained an automatic spot in the 12-driver field that advanced to the next round.
